    "description": {
      "description": "<p>Super adesivo químico de cura por fricção.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Uso:</span> Líquido, ou Arremesso.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Alcance:</span> 7/21m.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span> quando arremessado, ao chocar se espalha causando <em>Restrição</em>. Deve passar um teste de FIS (dif18) se soltar. O adesivo tem DR 24.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Preço:</span> 250 cobres.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Ofício:</span> Alquimia N4.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo para fabricar:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 6 horas.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Materiais:</span> 4<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;line-height:105%;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"> Reagentes.</span></p>",
